{"word":"ἱμάτιον","slug":"ἱμάτιον","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἱμάτιον, ου, τό</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <el>εἷμα</el> ‘garment’, <el>ἔννυμι</el> ‘to cover’] ‘covering for the body’<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b>in general, <b>clothing, apparel <a href='B:470 9:16'>Mt 9:16</a>; <a href='B:650 1:11'>Hb 1:11f</a>;</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pl.\">pl.</a> <b><a href='B:470 17:2'>Mt 17:2</a>; <a href='B:470 27:35'>27:35</a>; <a href='B:480 5:30'>Mk 5:30</a>; <a href='B:490 7:25'>Lk 7:25</a>; <a href='B:490 23:34'>23:34</a>; <a href='B:500 19:23'>J 19:23</a>; <a href='B:510 18:6'>Ac 18:6</a>; <a href='B:670 3:3'>1 Pt 3:3</a>; <a href='B:730 3:4'>Rv 3:4</a>; <a href='B:730 16:15'>16:15</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> of one’s outer garment, <b>cloak, coat</b> worn over the <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:χιτών\">χιτών</a></el> (the undergarment) <b><a href='B:470 9:20'>Mt 9:20f</a>; <a href='B:480 6:56'>Mk 6:56</a>; <a href='B:480 13:16'>13:16</a>; <a href='B:490 6:29'>Lk 6:29</a>; <a href='B:490 8:27'>8:27</a>; <a href='B:490 22:36'>22:36</a>; <a href='B:500 19:2'>J 19:2</a>; <a href='B:510 12:8'>Ac 12:8</a>; <a href='B:730 19:13'>Rv 19:13</a>, <a href='B:730 19:16'>16</a>;</b> the <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pl.\">pl.</a> <el>τὰ ἱμάτια</el> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ freq.\">freq.</a> involves a group of owners, as in <b><a href='B:470 21:7'>Mt 21:7f</a>; <a href='B:510 7:58'>Ac 7:58</a>; <a href='B:510 22:23'>22:23</a>; <a href='B:660 5:2'>Js 5:2</a></b> (<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ prob.\">prob.</a> a <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ ref.\">ref.</a> to exceptionally fine cloaks). <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἱματίζω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἱματισμός\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}